  "2165810": {
    "name": "Streets of Rogue 2",
    "steam_appid": 2165810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地痞街道2》（Streets of Rogue 2）盛情邀请你来到一个栩栩如生、万事难料开放世界中；在这里一切皆有可能。独自一人或是与朋友组队，踏上一场狂野冒险，以任何你想得到的方式来推翻腐败的总统！如果你喜欢专注于高自由度的故事生成游戏，例如《边缘世界》、《Valheim: 英灵神殿》、《星露谷物语》、《Kenshi》、《泰拉瑞亚》和《矮人要塞》，那么《地痞街道2》会让你觉得宾至如归。在这场引人入胜、独树一帜、由系统驱动的游戏体验里，玩家能够以无数种有趣的方式与全世界互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/2bfde47cf930ff07980b9ee0b21af88f.webp?t=1772094858\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/2bfde47cf930ff07980b9ee0b21af88f.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=65 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/9607358841b535a9b10bd5b6425d1365.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/9607358841b535a9b10bd5b6425d1365.webm?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/9607358841b535a9b10bd5b6425d1365.mp4?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让前作炙手可热的超高选择自由度在《地痞街道2》中得到了进化。我们正在依据着多年来无比珍贵的社区反馈意见来打造这款雄心勃勃的续作游戏，将具有无限可重复游玩性的深度roguelike玩法和RPG要素、沉浸式模拟的创造力结合在一起，目标是创造出最开放、最有趣的游戏体验。游戏具有数十个别具一格的职业，都各自拥有独特的特质与游玩风格，数之不尽的武器种类、工具、可摧毁的建筑，以及各种各样可劫持的载具。这是一个广袤无垠的游乐场，你可以在其中成为任何你想成为的人，制造任何你想要制造的混乱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/260457f85df67dcec14c3d0cc3b791bb.webp?t=1772094858\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/260457f85df67dcec14c3d0cc3b791bb.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=65 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/81a520f775b0e126f7b054466419f057.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/81a520f775b0e126f7b054466419f057.webm?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/81a520f775b0e126f7b054466419f057.mp4?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是推翻一位腐败的总统，夺下整个州郡的控制权，既可孤军奋战，也可以与朋友并肩作战。要如何行事，完全取决于你自己。想成为士兵、警察、科学家、黑客或是忍者？从众多独特的角色中挑选一位，或者创建独属于你自己的角色，在广阔的开放世界中肆意狂欢。雇一支雇佣军以谋政变；策划一场丧尸病毒大爆发；闯入市长办公室并将其挟为人质；建立超大的农场并成为难以忽视的商业巨鳄；召唤远古吸血鬼并贿赂其为你所用；或者就是进来随便玩玩，享受一下美好氛围，让主线任务一边儿去！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/188278ba1daef49e2ea37d2e2bc04efe.webp?t=1772094858\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/188278ba1daef49e2ea37d2e2bc04efe.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=65 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/09cca2591d64535ef65a804ae71b5718.poster.avif?t=1772094858\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/09cca2591d64535ef65a804ae71b5718.webm?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/09cca2591d64535ef65a804ae71b5718.mp4?t=1772094858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地痞街道2》的程序生成地图要比前作大上百倍。这个世界拥有多种多样的地点、完全可破坏的环境以及大量令人着迷的支线活动。霓虹都市、宁静乡村、神秘洞穴、阳光小岛、阴森墓地——探索这个栩栩如生的世界，与由先进AI控制的古怪居民互动，在每一次游戏中创造属于自己的、独一无二的冒险体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165810/extras/f6861125170dd8dd78ef0a8949037b03.avif?t=1772094858\" width=600 height=1350 /></span></p>",
